<p><b>Course Schedule</b> <br>
Week 1: Molecular Biology Primer <a href="http://www.math.ucsd.edu/~pcompeau/Ch03_Molecular_Biology_Primer_Edited.pdf">slides</a> <br>
Week 2: Genome Assembly <a href="http://www.nature.com/nbt/journal/v29/n11/full/nbt.2023.html">paper</a> <a href="https://www.dropbox.com/s/o5wjugo7v04lmm1/genomeassembly.pdf?dl=0">slides</a><br> 
Week 3: Finding Hidden Messages<br>
Week 4: Regulatory Motifs <br>
Week 5: Structure Prediction <br>
Week 6: Peptide Sequencing <br>
Week 7: Genome Rearrangement <br>
Week 8: PPI Networks <br>
Week 9: Sequence Alignment <br>
Week 10: Phylogeny <br>
Week 11: Hidden Markov Models <br>
Week 12: Machine Learning Algorithms <br>


